NAME().details: Provide a name for the inheriting contract.

NAME_COLORED().details: Returns `NAME` colored based logging the inheriting contract's role.

colorByRole(string).details: Returns `name` colored based logging its role.

startValidators().details: Uses any ETH held by the User to start validators on the beacon chain

returns._0: A list of created validator indices
returns._1: The amount of wei sent to the beacon chain
returns._2: The number of validators that have the MaxEB Note: If the user does not have enough ETH to start a validator, this method reverts Note: This method also advances one epoch forward on the beacon chain, so that withdrawal credential proofs are generated for each validator.
